        public UserInfo(java.lang.String name,
                Preferences pref,
                int cal,
                int distance,
                int floors,
                int steps,
                int actMin,
                int sedMin)
        Creates the UserInfo Object that stores information from API calls.
        Parameters:
        name - String the name of the user.
        pref - Preferences the Preference object for the custom dashboard.
        cal - int the lifetime total for calories.
        distance - int the lifetime total for distance.
        floors - the lifetime total for floors.
        steps - the lifetime total for steps.
        actMin - the lifetime total for active minutes.
        sedMin - the lifetime total for sedentary minutes.
